BRIEF-Knowit says inks frame agreement in Finland 
Oct 5 Knowit AB 
* Says inks frame agreement in Finland 
* Says agreement with KL-Kuntahankinnat Oy, which is owned by the Association of Finnish Local and Regional Authorities, acts as a central purchasing company on behalf of its regional and local government clientele Link to press release: here Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
